---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Contributor Spotlight: @jeremylongshore" description="Celebrating @jeremylongshore and Sugar — autonomous AI development for Claude Code.">
  <section class="spotlight-hero">
    <div class="container">
      <img src="images/spotlight-jeremylongshore.svg" alt="Contributor Spotlight: @jeremylongshore" class="banner" />
      <div class="meta">
        <span class="kicker">Contributor Spotlight</span>
        <h1>@jeremylongshore</h1>
        <p>
          Introducing <strong>Sugar</strong> — an autonomous AI development plugin that brings task orchestration,
          quality hooks, and MCP tools to Claude Code. Project‑scoped, safe, and powerful.
        </p>
        <div class="actions">
          <a class="btn" href="https://github.com/jeremylongshore/claude-code-plugins/pull/8" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">View PR #8</a>
          <a class="btn secondary" href="https://github.com/jeremylongshore/sugar" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Sugar Repository</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="details">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Why it matters</h2>
      <p>
        Sugar elevates Claude Code workflows with real task management, quality nudges, and a safe MCP bridge
        to the Python CLI. It’s a big step for the ecosystem — and a stellar first external contribution.
      </p>

      <h3>Install</h3>
      <pre><code>/plugin install sugar@claude-code-plugins-plus</code></pre>

      <h3>Learn more</h3>
      <ul>
        <li><a href="https://github.com/jeremylongshore/sugar" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Sugar Repository</a></li>
        <li><a href="https://github.com/jeremylongshore/claude-code-plugins/pull/8" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Pull Request #8</a></li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .spotlight-hero { padding: 1.25rem 0 0.5rem; }
  .banner { width: 100%; border: 1px solid var(--brand-light-gray); border-radius: 0.75rem; }
  .meta { margin-top: 1rem; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.5rem; }
  .kicker { color: var(--brand-orange); text-transform: uppercase; font-weight: 700; font-size: .85rem; letter-spacing: .04em; }
  h1 { margin: 0; }
  .actions { display: flex; gap: .75rem; margin-top: .25rem; }
  .btn { display: inline-flex; padding: .55rem .9rem; border-radius: .5rem; background: var(--brand-orange-dark); color: white; border: 1px solid var(--brand-orange); font-weight: 600; }
  .btn.secondary { background: transparent; border-color: var(--brand-light-gray); color: var(--brand-dark); }
  .details { padding: 1rem 0 2rem; }
  pre { background: var(--brand-light); border: 1px solid var(--brand-light-gray); border-radius: .5rem; padding: .75rem; overflow-x: auto; }
</style>
